This paper deals with the design of a secure wireless communication system, which involves signal processing and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves wireless communication and networking, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the second likely category. The paper also involves system design and optimization, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the third likely category. The paper also involves the use of intelligent reflecting surfaces, which suggests the category cs.MM (Multimedia) as the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy, which suggests the category cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the fifth likely category.
